Also awarded at the ceremony is the BBC Get Inspired Unsung Hero prize with the Welsh representative going on to compete against winners from the English regions, Northern Ireland and Scotland.
Nominations for this category close on 22 October and the overall winner will be announced at the BBC Sports Personality of the Year programme in Belfast on 20 December.
More details on the categories and how to nominate and vote are available at the Wales Sports Awards website.
